    "created_at": "2015-09-22T09:09:13Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-09-22T09:09:13Z",
    "body": "I tested this. This doesn’t seem to be about the new `title-bar-style` breaking anything; rather, `-webkit-app-region: drag` only seems to work for me with `frame: false`. This does feel like a bug, since the documentation doesn’t limit the dragging working only to frameless windows.\n\nI can definitely see how the drag behaviour would be useful with the new title bar styles as well. Not sure why it’s currently only working with a frameless window, need to dig around a bit more for this.\n"
  },
